{"title":"心中无数","authors":["路工"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":2,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中无数"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你皱皱眉头吸枝烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再把办公桌上计划书看一遍："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２．４．６．７数目字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５．６．８．３头痛开……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你肚内教条有半篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作经验也能拿出点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是遇到数字摇脑袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸吸烟来看时间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙上挂钟快五点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马上下班一天完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数字统计怎么办？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１、２、３、４凑起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你好像忘了干什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能凑合填一填？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经济工作数字最重要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小数点也不能错一点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（转载自《人民铁道》）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}